    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like gloss\u2014completely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The interior is equally immaculate, featuring premium leather upholstery with zero bolster wear and a cabin that remains smoke-free and fresh. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the adaptive cruise control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the vehicle sits on a set of matching high-performance tires with over 90% tread remaining. This is a turn-key example for the most discerning buyer who demands a vehicle in as-new condition.",
