    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s super clean inside and out and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 43500.0,
