    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. The subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension maintains factory geometry with fresh bushings and original damping characteristics, providing the quintessential analog driving experience. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue with a pristine interior, this vehicle remains in its original factory configuration with no aftermarket modifications or deferred maintenance. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning M-division purist.",
